    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Playing with this a bit, I find that I disagree with the premise of #12853.  Why should we show tooltips for e.g. the artillery attack cursor (or any of the other `UnitOrderGenerator` derived cursors), but not for e.g. the nuke cursor?  They are both area-of-effect weapons.  Trying to sort out and then maintain a working set of criteria for when to show or not show tooltips seems like a bigger headache than it is worth.\r\n\r\nFor context, the original games showed tooltips for everything (like we currently do):\r\n![screen shot 2017-04-10 at 21 03 03](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/167819/24880325/eec598ac-1e31-11e7-9f01-7bd6ac649204.png)\r\n"
  },
